description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;PART-TIME RECEPTIONIST REQUIRED&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are a busy, friendly, caring practice who are part of Erewash Health Partnership, which includes 9 other surgeries within the Ilkeston and Long Eaton areas, with a list size of 5,000 patients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are currently looking to recruit a &lt;strong&gt;part-time 25hrs per week&lt;/strong&gt; Receptionist to join our team of 4 other receptionists. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;General practice experience and an understanding of the NHS is essential, together with experience in patient management, patient records, reception work and a working knowledge of the computer package SystmOne.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The hours of work will be on a shift basis and the successful candidate will be expected to be able to work during and cover the full range of surgery hours between 0800-1830 during their shifts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are under Agenda for Change and this banding will be used, alongside the successful applicants experience when looking at the salary.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applications should &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;only&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; be submitted via NHS Jobs, if you have any issues accessing this site or have any questions please contact Diane Young, Practice Manager on 07891 229768.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The closing date is Monday 9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;th&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; November 2020&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Interviews dates are TBC. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
